            <title><![CDATA[【Hi-Talk】“语通四海，文润五洲”第二届国际中文日文化体验活动预告]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【Hi-Talk】“语通四海，文润五洲”第二届国际中文日文化体验活动预告]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/18/120930</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/18/120930</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 18:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;be452972-e844-4a01-88f8-3041a435dd99&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/18/1744955291433.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;语言是促进各国人民相知相亲、增进不同文明交流互鉴的桥梁。4月21日，国际教育学院将以“语通四海，文润五洲”为主题举办“国际中文日”文化体验活动。活动旨在庆祝和推广国际中文日，通过语言文字闯关游戏和文化体验活动深入感知中国语言文字和传统文化的魅力，促进中外文化交流。活动安排如下：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;Language serves as a bridge to foster mutual understanding among people of different nations and to promote exchanges and mutual learning among diverse civilizations. On April 21, College of International Education will host a cultural experience event titled &quot;Language Connects the World, Culture Enriches the Globe&quot; to celebrate and promote International Chinese Language Day. Through language-based challenge games and cultural activities, the event aims to provide participants with an immersive experience of the charm of the Chinese language and traditional culture, while fostering cultural exchanges between China and other countries. The event details are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;一、活动时间和地点&amp;nbsp; Event Time and Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;_Toc9556&quot; id=&quot;_Toc9556&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;4月21日10:30-13:30&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;April 21, 10:30 AM–1:30 PM&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;一校区步行街&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Pedestrian Street, Campus One&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;二、主办单位Organizer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;学生工作部（处）/团委&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;Student Affairs Department/Committee of HIT Communist Youth League&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;校工会&amp;nbsp; Hit Faculty and Staff Union&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;国际教育学院 College of International Education&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;三、参与人员&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Participants&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;全体师生&amp;nbsp; All faculty and students are welcome.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;四、活动介绍&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Event Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;本次活动现场设置8个活动环节，每个区域前有活动介绍。参与者在签到处领取集章册，完成每个环节集章一个，前200个集满4个章的参与者可以获得哈工大主题冰箱贴一枚，前100个集满8个章的参与者可以获得糖画或面塑一个。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;The event will feature 8 interactive stations, each with its own introduction. Participants can collect a stamp booklet at the registration desk. For every station completed, they will receive one stamp. The first 200 participants collecting four stamps will receive a HIT-themed refrigerator magnet, while the first 100 participants collecting all eight stamps will receive either a sugar painting or a dough figurine.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;五、活动环节&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Event Stations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;1.字游列国，文通天下——文字闯关&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;2.一言为定，语见世界——口语闯关&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;3.四海同音，华彩共赏——中文音乐&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;4.字里行间，文明千年——汉字听写&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;5.汉服雅集，霓裳焕彩——汉服体验&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;6.矢入壶欢，语脉相连——投壶体验&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;7.彩墨脸谱，演绎古今——脸谱体验&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;8.糖凝锦绣，面塑山河——糖画面塑&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Travel Through Characters, Connect the World&quot; – Writing Challenge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;A Word Seals the Deal, Language Meets the World&quot; – Speaking Challenge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Shared Melodies, Splendid Chinese&quot; – Chinese Music&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Between the Lines, Millennia of Civilization&quot; – Chinese Dictation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Elegant Han Chinese Clothing Gathering, Radiant Attire&quot; – Han Chinese Clothing Experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Arrows in the Pot, Language Links Hearts&quot; – Arrow Tossing Game&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Colorful Opera Masks, Bridging Past and Present&quot; – Mask Painting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-left:8px; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;tab-stops:list 36.0pt&quot;&gt;&quot;Sugar Art, Ancient Delights&quot; – Sugar Painting Craft&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;79ad33b3-ef1a-4c70-82ea-d980de691c0d&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/18/1744955430199.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;欢迎广大师生共庆国际中文日，欣赏中华文化之美&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;All faculty and students are invited to celebrate International Chinese Language Day and to appreciate the beauty of Chinese culture.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;注：通知以中文版为准，英文翻译仅供参考。最终解释权归国际教育学院所有。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt&quot;&gt;Note: The Chinese version of this notice shall prevail. The English translation is for reference only. The College of International Education reserves the final right of interpretation.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
